  <data name="Discord_Feature_Updates_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>Real-time Updates</value></data>
  <data name="Discord_Feature_Updates_Desc" xml:space="preserve"><value>Never miss a beat. Get instant notifications about new VTuber debuts, lore updates, and major wiki revisions before anyone else.</value></data>
  <data name="Discord_Feature_Events_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>Community Events</value></data>
  <data name="Discord_Feature_Events_Desc" xml:space="preserve"><value>Participate in organized watch parties, gaming nights, and community art contests. Connect with fans who share your oshi.</value></data>
  <data name="Discord_Feature_EditorHelp_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>Help for Editors</value></data>
  <data name="Discord_Feature_EditorHelp_Desc" xml:space="preserve"><value>Direct access to veteran editors. Get real-time help with formatting, sourcing, and image optimization for your favorite wiki pages.</value></data>
  <data name="Discord_Feature_Roles_Title" xml:space="preserve"><value>Exclusive Roles</value></data>
